The paper deals with lower bounds for computational problems, which suggests that it may belong to the category of Computational Complexity (cs.CC). The use of Subset Sum and scheduling problems suggests that it may also belong to the categories of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM). The paper also uses techniques from graph theory and optimization, which suggests that it may belong to the categories of Game Theory (cs.GT) and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
